snippet.title: Game & Watch - Lion (c)1981 Nintendo [MAME emulation footage]
snippet.description: Support for this will be in MAME 0.215, thanks to algestam for the emulation and hydef for the artwork.  Artwork can be found at https://drive.google.com/open?id=1WLKcvynl0ky2mRL1UacA9yaiMTnNs4x5
